content.value: Define the period for which your data can be stored on the platform
Set how often the data retention job runs to clean up expired data based on the above specified retention period. Default frequency is set as ‘Daily’.

The Data Retention Policy feature allows you to manage how long your data is stored on our platform. Set your desired retention period in months. Our system will automatically delete data older than the specified time frame. You can update this setting at any time to adjust your retention policy. Remember to consider legal requirements, balance operational needs, and regularly review your retention period.
Specify the number of days your data will be stored on our platform before automatic deletion. Enter whole numbers only.
Value must be between one(1) day and the maximum limit of your Data Retention Package.
Please confirm before applying any changes to data retention settings
